video_name: Polres Metro Bekasi Ungkap Kasus Persetubuhan dan Kekerasan Seksual dalam Lingkup Rumah Tangga Bekasi, 29 September 2025 – Polres Metro Bekasi mengungkap kasus persetubuhan dan kekerasan seksual dalam lingkup rumah tangga yang dilakukan pria berinisial MR (52), seorang ustadz atau mubaligh. Press release dipimpin Kapolres Metro Bekasi KBP Mustofa, S.I.K., M.H. di Lobby Utama Mako Polres Metro Bekasi, Senin (29/9). Kasus ini terungkap setelah laporan korban pada Juli 2025. Hasil penyidikan menunjukkan tersangka mencabuli anak angkat dan keponakannya sejak mereka masih remaja. Dari tangan pelaku, polisi menyita barang bukti berupa ponsel dan flashdisk berisi rekaman. Tersangka dijerat UU Perlindungan Anak, UU TPKS, dan UU PKDRT dengan ancaman hukuman hingga 15 tahun penjara serta denda Rp5 miliar. Kapolres Metro Bekasi menegaskan komitmennya menindak tegas pelaku kekerasan seksual. “Tidak ada seorang pun yang kebal hukum, apalagi menyangkut kejahatan seksual terhadap anak maupun dalam rumah tangga. Polres Metro Bekasi berkomitmen melindungi korban serta memberikan rasa aman kepada masyarakat,” ujarnya. #viraltiktok #tiktokviral #bekasi #pelecehanperempuan #fyppppppppppppppppppppppp

video_name: Polsek Cikarang Selatan Berhasil Ungkap Kasus Perampasan Motor, Empat Pelaku Diamankan dan Satu DPO Bekasi – Jajaran Polsek Cikarang Selatan berhasil mengungkap kasus tindak pidana perampasan kendaraan bermotor roda dua (R2) sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 368 KUHPidana. Dalam pengungkapan ini, empat pelaku berhasil ditangkap, sementara satu pelaku lain masih berstatus DPO. Peristiwa perampasan ini terjadi pada Jumat, 19 September 2025 pukul 22.45 WIB di Jalan Pintu Keluar Parkiran Orange Country Meikarta, Desa Cibatu, Kecamatan Cikarang Selatan, Kabupaten Bekasi. Korban bernama Sarkawi (42), seorang karyawan swasta asal Kota Serang Baru, terpaksa kehilangan sepeda motornya setelah dihadang kawanan pelaku dengan senjata tajam. Kapolsek Cikarang Selatan, AKP Erwin Setiawan, S.I.K., M.H, menjelaskan korban baru pulang kerja ketika dihampiri tiga orang tak dikenal. “Pelaku menggunakan sepeda motor dan membawa senjata tajam jenis celurit untuk mengancam korban agar menyerahkan motornya. Karena nyawanya terancam, korban melarikan diri dan meninggalkan motor di TKP. Laporan korban langsung kami tindak lanjuti dengan olah TKP dan penyelidikan,” ungkap Kapolsek. Unit Reskrim Polsek Cikarang Selatan yang dipimpin IPTU Fifin Edi Hermawan, S.H. (Kanit Reskrim) bersama tim Opsnal kemudian bergerak cepat. Berdasarkan analisis CCTV dan keterangan sumber di lapangan, salah satu pelaku bernama Eki bin Udin Abidin (33) berhasil diamankan di sekitar Stasiun Lemahabang pada Sabtu, 20 September 2025. Menurut Kanit Reskrim, Eki merupakan residivis yang sebelumnya pernah terlibat kasus membawa kabur motor korban lain pada 12 Agustus 2025. Selain Eki, polisi juga mengamankan tiga pelaku lainnya yakni Haikal Nanda Priyatna (18), warga Karangsari Cikarang Timur yang berperan sebagai eksekutor; Farhan Febrian (20), warga Waluya Cikarang Utara yang meminjamkan motor untuk aksi sekaligus menerima bagian uang; dan Irgi Irawan (21), warga Sukaraya Karang Bahagia yang membantu menjual hasil rampasan. Sementara itu, satu pelaku lain bernama Beni masih buron dan masuk daftar pencarian orang (DPO). Barang bukti yang berhasil diamankan antara lain 1 unit motor Honda Beat, 2 unit handphone (Samsung dan Vivo), serta 1 bilah celurit. Kanit Reskrim IPTU Fifin Edi Hermawan menegaskan pihaknya masih terus memburu pelaku DPO. “Beni yang membawa motor hasil rampasan masih dalam pengejaran. Kami minta agar segera menyerahkan diri. Kasus ini juga masih kami kembangkan untuk memastikan apakah ada TKP lain yang melibatkan para pelaku,” jelasnya. Atas perbuatannya, para pelaku dijerat dengan Pasal 368 KUHPidana tentang Tindak Pidana Perampasan, dengan ancaman hukuman maksimal sembilan tahun penjara. “Polsek Cikarang Selatan berkomitmen memberantas segala bentuk kejahatan jalanan demi menjaga keamanan dan ketertiban di wilayah hukum kami. Kami juga mengimbau masyarakat untuk tidak segan melapor bila mengalami tindak kriminal serupa,” tutup Kapolsek Erwin. #bekasi #fypage #tiktokviral #viraltiktok #begal

video_name: Polsek Cikarang Selatan Tindaklanjuti Aduan Warga Terkait Warung Diduga Jual Obat Terlarang di Desa Serang, Kapolsek : Jika Ada Aktifitas Laporkan Cikarang Selatan – Polsek Cikarang Selatan bergerak cepat menindaklanjuti aduan masyarakat terkait adanya warung yang diduga menjual obat-obatan terlarang golongan G di wilayah Desa Serang, Kecamatan Cikarang Selatan, Kabupaten Bekasi, Rabu (24/9/2025). Laporan tersebut diterima sekitar pukul 11.00 WIB dan segera ditindaklanjuti oleh Unit Reskrim Polsek Cikarang Selatan dengan melakukan pengecekan di beberapa titik yang dilaporkan warga. Di antaranya dekat Balai Desa Serang, Kampung Cijingga, kawasan Blok J Jati Raya, serta sepanjang Jalan KH. Ma’mun Nawawi Desa Serang. Kegiatan ini dipimpin oleh IPTU Fifin Edi Hermawan, S.H. (Kanit Reskrim), didampingi IPDA Iyus A. (Panit Opsnal), serta anggota Opsnal Polsek Cikarang Selatan. Kanit Reskrim Polsek Cikarang Selatan, IPTU Fifin Edi Hermawan, S.H., menuturkan bahwa pihaknya menindaklanjuti laporan warga dengan serius. “Begitu kami menerima laporan masyarakat, tim langsung turun ke lokasi-lokasi yang dimaksud. Dari hasil pengecekan, warung yang dilaporkan sudah tidak beroperasi dan tidak ditemukan aktivitas penjualan obat-obatan golongan G,” jelas IPTU Fifin. Kapolsek Cikarang Selatan, AKP Erwin Setiawan, S.I.K., M.H., menambahkan bahwa pihaknya akan terus menindaklanjuti laporan warga dan memperketat pengawasan.  “Bagi warga yang melihat aktivitas perdagangan obat terlarang di Cikarang Selatan, khususnya di Desa Serang, silakan segera lapor kepada pihak kepolisian Polsek Cikarang Selatan,” tegas Kapolsek. #fypage #tiktokviral #fyppppppppppppppppppppppp #cikarang #bekasi

video_name: Polsek Cikarang Timur mengungkap kasus tindak pidana pemerasan dengan ancaman dan penadahan kendaraan bermotor yang dilakukan komplotan pelaku dengan modus mengaku sebagai debt collector. Empat orang tersangka berhasil diamankan, sementara empat lainnya masih dalam pengejaran. Wakapolres Metro Bekasi, AKBP Apri Fajar menjelaskan, pengungkapan ini merupakan respons atas maraknya laporan masyarakat terkait aksi perampasan kendaraan roda dua di wilayah Cikarang Timur. “Dari hasil penyelidikan, kami menangkap empat tersangka yakni Rasim alias Mandor, Cecep Supriyadi alias Cecep, Hendri Purwanto alias Hendri, dan Ikhsan Rizky Saputra alias Putra,” ujar Apri Fajar dalam konferensi pers, Selasa (30/9/2025). Sementara itu, empat pelaku lainnya telah masuk dalam daftar pencarian orang (DPO). Mereka adalah Rohidin alias Gareng, Robi alias Komeng, Aday, dan Basan. Apri membeberkan bahwa para pelaku berpura-pura sebagai petugas leasing yang menagih kendaraan milik korban karena alasan tunggakan cicilan. Mereka kemudian menghadang korban di jalan, melakukan intimidasi, hingga kendaraan diserahkan secara paksa. “Setelah berhasil merampas motor, kendaraan tersebut dibawa oleh joki ke lokasi penampungan. Rencananya, beberapa unit akan dikirim ke Lampung,” terang Apri. Dari pengungkapan ini, polisi menyita sejumlah barang bukti, di antaranya 8 unit sepeda motor berbagai jenis dan 1 unit mobil truk putih yang digunakan untuk mengangkut motor, dan beberapa unit ponsel yang digunakan pelaku dalam aksi kejahatan. Disebutkan, kendaraan-kendaraan tersebut belum sempat dijual atau dikirim ke luar daerah. Semua masih berada dalam tahap persiapan saat diamankan. #tiktokviral #fyppppppppppppppppppppppp #cikarang #bekasi #debtcollector

video_name: Polsek Cikarang Barat berhasil mengungkap kasus penganiayaan yang berujung kematian di kawasan Cikarang Barat, Kabupaten Bekasi. Seorang pria berinisial RA, berusia 29 tahun, yang berprofesi sebagai tukang cukur asal Kota Banjar, Jawa Barat, ditetapkan sebagai tersangka atas tewasnya rekannya sendiri, EP (26), warga Garut. Peristiwa berdarah ini terjadi di sebuah kontrakan di Kampung Cibitung, Desa Telagaasih, pada Sabtu dini hari, 27 September 2025. Korban sempat dilarikan ke rumah sakit, namun akhirnya meninggal dunia dua hari kemudian akibat luka tusuk di perut, tangan, dan paha. Kapolres Metro Bekasi, Kombes Pol Mustofa, menjelaskan, pelaku berhasil ditangkap setelah sempat melarikan diri ke kediamannya di Kota Banjar, Jawa Barat. Dari hasil penyelidikan, motif pelaku diduga karena cemburu, lantaran korban memiliki kedekatan dengan seorang wanita yang juga dikenal keduanya. Polisi menyita sebilah pisau badik sebagai barang bukti. Kini, pelaku RA dijerat Pasal 351 ayat 3 KUHP, dengan ancaman pidana maksimal tujuh tahun penjara. #cikarang #bekasi #fyppppppppppppppppppppppp #tiktokviral #viraltiktok

video_name: Am Mittwoch (24.09.2025) ereignete sich auf der A6 bei Immeldorf (Landkreis Ansbach) ein schwerer Arbeitsunfall. Bei Abrissarbeiten war ein Teil einer Brücke, welche abgerissen werden sollte, auf die Fahrerkabine eines Baggers gestürzt. Der Fahrer kam dabei ums Leben. Kollegen hatten noch versucht, das tonnenschwere Betonteil unter anderem mit weiteren Baggern anzuheben und dem Mann zu helfen. Mit den vorhandenen Maschinen war das wegen des Gewichts aber nicht möglich. Der genaue Unfallhergang war zunächst unklar. Zahlreiche Einsatzkräfte von THW, Feuerwehr, Polizei und Rettungsdienst waren an der Unfallstelle vor Ort. Die Baustelle wurde gestoppt und die Polizei nahm die Ermittlungen auf. Die Bergungsmaßnahmen dauerten knapp 6 Stunden.

video_name: Schüsse und Explosion in München Im Münchner Norden läuft seit den frühen Morgenstunden ein Großeinsatz von Polizei und Feuerwehr. Auch Spezialeinheiten und Sprengstoff-Experten sind vor Ort. Nach ersten Informationen hat es mehrere Explosionen gegeben, außerdem sollen Schüsse gefallen sein. Eine männliche Leiche wurde entdeckt. Nach ersten Informationen soll der Mann sein Elternhaus mit Sprengsätzen präpariert, in Brand gesetzt und anschließend Suizid begangen haben. Mindestens eine weitere Person wurde mit Schussverletzungen aufgefunden. Der Einsatzort liegt an der Lerchenauer Straße. Die Polizei hat das Gebiet weiträumig abgesperrt und bittet Anwohner und Autofahrer, den Bereich zu meiden. Eine große Rauchwolke ist schon von weitem sichtbar. #news #polizei #münchen

video_name: Große Angst in München nach Explosionen und Schüsse - Oktoberfest bleibt geschlossen - Das ist ein Update und hier sind alle Informationen die wir bisher wissen Im Münchener Norden läuft seit den frühen Morgenstunden ein Großeinsatz von Polizei und Feuerwehr. Hintergrund sind Explosionen, Schüsse und ein Brand in einem Wohnhaus. Auch Spezialeinheiten und Sprengstoff-Experten sind im Einsatz. Er soll zudem einen Rucksack bei sich getragen haben, in dem möglicherweise eine weitere Sprengfalle versteckt ist. Entschärfer sind vor Ort. Der Einsatzbereich ist weiträumig abgesperrt. Schulen in der Nähe bleiben geschlossen. Brisant: Die Polizei prüft auch einen möglichen Zusammenhang mit dem Münchener Oktoberfest. In einem Brief des mutmaßlichen Täters sollen Hinweise enthalten sein, die ernst genommen werden. Deshalb bleibt das Oktoberfest am heutigen Mittwoch zunächst bis 17 Uhr geschlossen. Die Ermittlungen laufen derzeit in alle Richtungen. Die Polizei bittet Anwohner, den Bereich im Münchener Norden unbedingt zu meiden. #news #polizei #münchen #oktoberfest

video_name: Auf der A3 in Bayern kam es am Montagnachmittag zu einem schweren Zwischenfall. Zwischen Geiselwind und Schlüsselfeld stürzte eine Hochspannungsleitung auf die Fahrbahn.Auslöser war ein Bagger, der bei Böschungsarbeiten eine 20-Kilovolt-Leitung beschädigte. Diese riss ab und fiel auf die Autobahn. Verletzt wurde glücklicherweise niemand.Die Einsatzkräfte sperrten sofort beide Fahrtrichtungen. Nachdem die Leitung von der Fahrbahn entfernt war, stellte man fest, dass auch weitere Kabel beschädigt waren. Deshalb mussten sie vollständig demontiert werden.Die Folge: eine Vollsperrung bis in die Nachtstunden – und massives Verkehrschaos nicht nur auf der A3, sondern auch auf den Ausweichrouten. Besonders im Raum Schlüsselfeld kam es zu erheblichen Behinderungen.Erst gegen 23 Uhr konnte die Autobahn wieder freigegeben werden.

video_name: In Gyhum im Landkreis Rotenburg kam es in den frühen Morgenstunden des Mittwochs, den 24. September 2025, zu einem Tötungsdelikt. Eine 30-jährige Frau stirb nach einem mutmaßlichen Angriff im Rahmen einer Auseinandersetzung mit ihrem vier Jahre älteren Partner. Der Tatverdächtige meldete sich nach der Tat selbst bei der Polizei. In der Nähe des Tatortes kam es in derselben Nacht zu einem Brand an einem landwirtschaftlichen Anwesen. Die Polizei prüft derzeit, ob ein Zusammenhang zwischen beiden Vorfällen besteht. Die Ermittlungen dauern an: Beweismittel werden gesichert, Zeugen befragt und Videomaterial ausgewertet. Bekannt ist, dass der mutmaßliche Täter vor Ort kein Unbekannter war. Er ist Landwirt und Mitglied der Freiwilligen Feuerwehr, war jedoch nicht in dem Betrieb tätig, in dem der Brand ausbrach. Nachbarn beschreiben das Opfer und ihren Lebensgefährten als nette, freundliche Menschen. Sie zeigten sich schockiert über die Tat, da es zwischen den beiden offenbar nie Streit gab und sie immer gemeinsam unterwegs waren.

video_name: Brunsbüttel in Schleswig-Holstein. Ein vier Monate altes Mädchen ist tot. Die Eltern – beide 24 Jahre alt – sitzen in Untersuchungshaft. Der Vorwurf: Mord durch Unterlassen. Nach bisherigen Erkenntnissen sollen sie ihr Baby verhungern lassen haben. Am 26. September rief das Paar selbst die Feuerwehr. Doch für das Kind kam jede Hilfe zu spät – ein Notarzt konnte nur noch den Tod feststellen. Das Amtsgericht Itzehoe erließ Haftbefehl, die Staatsanwaltschaft spricht vom Mordmerkmal der Grausamkeit. Im Haushalt leben außerdem zweijährige Zwillinge. Sie wurden in die Obhut des Jugendamts gebracht. Nachbarn berichten von häufigem Babyschreien und einem verwahrlosten Haus. Jetzt steht auch das Jugendamt in der Kritik. Angehörige und Nachbarn sprechen von Versagen der Behörden. Das Amt selbst verweist auf das laufende Verfahren und äußert sich nicht. Die Ermittlungen zu den genauen Umständen dauern an. #news #baby #polizei

bio: Akun Resmi Metropolitan.id  business
video_name: Suasana haru bercampur tegang mewarnai proses evakuasi ambruknya Pondok Pesantren (Ponpes) Al-Khoziny, Sidoarjo, Jawa Timur, Senin sore (29/9).  Di tengah reruntuhan beton yang menutup akses, seorang anggota Tim Rescue DPKP Surabaya, Aziz, berhasil menjalin komunikasi dengan dua santri yang masih hidup di balik puing. Aziz mendengar suara Yusuf (16) dan Haikal dari sela-sela bangunan yang runtuh. Dalam percakapan singkat itu, Yusuf mengatakan dirinya tidak terluka parah meski perutnya terjepit beton. Sementara Haikal mengaku seluruh tubuhnya terasa sakit akibat tertindih puing. Dengan suara tenang, Aziz terus memberi semangat agar keduanya tidak panik dan tetap sadar. “Tetap kuat, jangan tidur ya. Kami akan segera sampai,” ucap Aziz melalui celah sempit puing sebelum melaporkan posisi korban kepada tim lainnya via handy talkie. Hingga Selasa sore (30/9), tim penyelamat masih berupaya mengevakuasi ratusan santri yang tertimbun, dengan tiga orang telah dipastikan meninggal dunia. Proses evakuasi diperkirakan membutuhkan waktu lebih lama karena kondisi reruntuhan yang menumpuk hingga lantai dasar. Video: Rescue DPKP Surabaya .  #ponesambruk #ponpesalkhoziny #sidoarjo #rescuedpkpsurabaya #surabaya

bio: Akun Resmi Metropolitan.id  business
video_name: Menteri Keuangan Purbaya Yudhi Sadewa melontarkan kritik keras kepada PT Pertamina yang dinilai lamban dalam membangun kilang minyak baru.  Menurutnya, ketergantungan Indonesia terhadap impor BBM tak kunjung berkurang lantaran proyek kilang tidak berjalan optimal. “Pertamina ini kelihatannya malas-malasan bangun kilang. Kalau tidak ada kemajuan, saya potong dananya, bahkan kalau perlu saya ganti Dirutnya,” tegas Purbaya dalam rapat kerja dengan Komisi XI DPR, Selasa (30/9). Purbaya menilai, kapasitas kilang dalam negeri tidak sebanding dengan kebutuhan konsumsi nasional.  Akibatnya, Indonesia masih banyak membeli BBM dari luar negeri, terutama Singapura. Ia menegaskan pembangunan kilang baru adalah langkah strategis untuk memperkuat ketahanan energi nasional sekaligus mengurangi beban subsidi. 🎥: TVR Parlemen #metropolitanid #bacametropolitanid #menkeupurbaya #sebutpertaminamalas #imporsingapura #kilangminyak

bio: Akun Resmi Metropolitan.id  business
video_name: Kebakaran melanda Hunian Pekerja Konstruksi (HPK) 1 Tower 14 di kawasan Ibu Kota Nusantara (IKN), Rabu (1/10/2025) petang. Api sempat membesar dan menimbulkan kepulan asap tebal yang terlihat dari sekitar lokasi. Plt Deputi Sarana dan Prasarana Otorita IKN, Danis H. Sumadilaga, membenarkan peristiwa tersebut.  Menurutnya, sejumlah unit mobil pemadam kebakaran langsung diterjunkan untuk menjinakkan api. “Api sudah berhasil dipadamkan,” ujarnya. Hingga saat ini, pihak Otorita IKN maupun aparat terkait masih melakukan pendataan. Belum ada keterangan resmi mengenai penyebab kebakaran maupun apakah terdapat korban dalam peristiwa tersebut. Hunian pekerja konstruksi sendiri merupakan fasilitas tempat tinggal sementara bagi ribuan pekerja yang tengah membangun sejumlah infrastruktur utama di kawasan inti IKN. Video: Ist.  #ibukotanusantara #ibukotanusantarakebakaran #hunianiknkebakaran #kebakaran #metropolitanid

bio: Akun Resmi Metropolitan.id  business
video_name: Sejumlah wali murid SDIT Al Izzah, Kota Serang, menyatakan penolakan terhadap program Makan Bergizi Gratis (MBG) yang dibagikan di sekolah. Mereka menilai, mayoritas orang tua sudah membayar biaya masuk, SPP, dan layanan katering, sehingga merasa tidak perlu menerima program tersebut. Selain itu, para wali murid juga menolak keberadaan dapur dan aktivitas distribusi MBG di lingkungan sekolah. Menurut mereka, hal itu berpotensi menimbulkan masalah baru seperti penumpukan sampah, risiko kecelakaan, hingga persoalan keamanan. Menanggapi hal ini, Wali Kota Serang Budi Rustandi menegaskan tetap mendukung program nasional MBG. Namun ia memahami bila sekolah dari kalangan keluarga mampu lebih memilih menggunakan katering yang sudah berjalan jauh sebelum program ini hadir. 🎥: TikTok/viralinaja #metropolitanid #bacametropolitan #walimuridsditalizzah #tolakmbgdisekolah #kateringsendiri

bio: Akun Resmi Metropolitan.id  business
video_name: Presiden Republik Indonesia, Prabowo Subianto, menyampaikan pidato dalam Musyawarah Nasional (Munas) Partai Keadilan Sejahtera (PKS) di Jakarta pada Senin, 29 September 2025. Dalam pidatonya, Prabowo menyoroti keberhasilan program makan bergizi gratis (MBG) yang telah berjalan selama 11 bulan. Program ini diklaim berhasil menjangkau 30 juta penerima manfaat. Para penerima manfaat tersebut terdiri dari anak-anak dan ibu hamil di seluruh Indonesia. Prabowo menegaskan bahwa program makan bergizi gratis merupakan salah satu program unggulan pemerintahannya. Menurutnya, program ini berhasil menyelamatkan anggaran negara sebesar Rp300 triliun. Video: YT/PKSTV #presiden #prabowosubianto #presidenprabowo #makanbergizigratis #mbg #munaspks #metropolitanid #bacametropolitan

bio: Akun Resmi Metropolitan.id  business
video_name: Presiden RI Prabowo Subianto menegaskan bahwa dirinya tidak akan segan menindak kepala daerah yang melakukan pelanggaran, meski berasal dari partai politiknya sendiri. Pesan itu disampaikan saat meresmikan akad massal 26 ribu rumah subsidi di Cileungsi, Kabupaten Bogor, Senin (29/9/2025). Dalam kesempatan itu, Prabowo secara khusus menyebut Gubernur Jawa Barat, Dedi Mulyadi, yang merupakan kader Partai Gerindra. Ia memberi peringatan kepada bawahannya agar berhati-hati dalam menjalankan tugas sebagai pemimpin daerah. “Gubernur Jawa Barat kebetulan Gerindra, tapi kalau brengsek saya usut kau. Tapi saya yakin kau tidak brengsek. Tapi jangan salah, saya tahu ada kader-kader Gerindra yang begitu jadi bupati, wali kota, apa itu istilahnya itu petantang-petenteng,” ucap Prabowo. Prabowo menekankan bahwa pemimpin harus ikhlas, tulus, dan tidak bersikap egois. Ia mengingatkan kebijakan yang tidak berpihak kepada rakyat dapat memicu gejolak. 🎥: YT Sekretariat Presiden #metropolitanid #bacametropolitan #presidenprabowo #guberjurjabarkdm #candaanprabowokekdm #perumahansubsidicileungsi

bio: Akun Resmi Metropolitan.id  business
video_name: Menteri Keuangan Purbaya Yudhi Sadewa, mengungkapkan bahwa harga keekonomian elpiji dan Bahan Bakar Minyak (BBM) sebenarnya jauh lebih tinggi dari harga jual. Menurut Purbaya, harga asli elpiji 3 kilogram mencapai Rp42.750, bukan Rp12.750 per tabung seperti yang saat ini dibayarkan masyarakat.  Selisih sekitar Rp30.000 per tabung ditanggung oleh pemerintah melalui skema subsidi maupun kompensasi energi. Begitupun untuk BBM jenis solar dan pertalite. Purbaya menegaskan, subsidi ini diberikan agar daya beli masyarakat tetap terjaga di tengah kondisi ekonomi yang belum sepenuhnya stabil. 🎥: TVR Parlemen #metropolitanid #bacametropolitanid #menkeupurbaya #purbayayudhisadewa #gaselpijidanbbm #subsidipemerintah

Terima kasih yang sebesar-besarnya kepada @Wipol Indonesia dan @Vixal Anti Kerak atas dukungan dalam menjaga kebersihan masjid dan mushola di berbagai daerah. video_name: ? Caso Beatriz - Em 2015, a menina Beatriz Angélica Mota, de 7 anos, desapareceu durante a formatura da irmã em um colégio tradicional de Petrolina. Pouco depois, ela foi encontrada sem vida em uma sala desativada da escola. O caso gerou grande comoção e mobilizou milhares de pessoas em busca de respostas. Anos depois, em 2022, exames de DNA identificaram Marcelo da Silva como autor. Já preso por outros delitos, ele confessou o ato. A confirmação encerrou parte das dúvidas, mas familiares e autoridades ainda levantam questionamentos sobre falhas nas investigações e possíveis participações de outras pessoas. . . . . . ? video_name: ? Caso Serrambi - Thais Furlan fala sobre o caso Serrambi. O caso em que Maria Eduarda Dourado e Tarsila Gusmão desapareceram após um passeio de lancha em Porto de Galinhas, durante um fim de semana com amigos em Serrambi. Depois de se separarem do grupo, foram vistas pegando carona e, segundo uma testemunha, elas pegaram uma Kombi perto de uma padaria. Dez dias depois, os corpos foram encontrados em um canavial no distrito de Camela, pelo próprio pai de Tarsila. As investigações apontaram dois irmãos kombeiros como principais suspeitos, com testemunhas, perícias e objetos que ligavam o veículo à cena. Apesar dos indícios, Marcelo e Valfrido Lira foram absolvidos em júri popular em 2010, e a decisão foi mantida em todas as instâncias. Até hoje, o caso segue oficialmente sem solução. . . . . . ? video_name: Hungarian Goulash | Soups So Good It Can Cure Any Sickness Ep. 13 INGREDIENTS: Hungarian Goulash - 1 kg beef chuck, cut into cubes  - 1 white onion, diced  - 9-12 garlic cloves, minced  - 1/3 cup of paprika  - 1 tbsp of caraway seeds - 2 green bell peppers, chopped  - 1 red bell pepper, chopped  - 1 cup tomatoes, chopped  - Beef stock to fill the pot  - 1 potato, chopped  - 1 carrot, chopped  - Salt and pepper to taste - Oil/lard for frying  INSTRUCTIONS: - Start by seasoning your meat with salt and pepper and slice into bite sized cubes.  - In a hot soup pot sauté your garlic and onions until softened. Add your meat and season with paprika and caraway seeds. Mix until everything is combined.  - Add your chopped bell peppers along with tomatoes and mix.  - Add beef stock until the pot is filled and allow to simmer for 1-1.5 hrs minutes or until meat is tender before adding the rest of your vegetables. Season with salt and pepper. - Serve with chopped parsley and enjoy!  #Soups #asmr #ASMRCooking

Add tomato paste and stir until well combined before adding celery and leaves along with the spices. - Add lentils, chickpeas, crushed tomatoes, and beef broth until the pot is full. let cook for about 40 mins or until lentils are soft. - Add your cilantro and parsley and vermicelli noodles. Season with salt and pepper. cook for about 15mins. - add your flour slurry to thicken the soup. - Serve with a squeeze of lemon and enjoy! #Soups #asmr #cookingasmr

video_name: 🇬🇷 Avgolemono | Soups So Good It Can Cure Any Sickness Ep. 14 INGREDIENTS:  Greek Avgolemono: - 5-8 chicken thigh bone in, (can also be 1 whole chicken) - Olive oil - 1 tbsp of Italian seasoning - 1 whole onion, diced - 5-10 garlic cloves, minced - 3/4 cup celery, diced - 1 carrot, diced - Chicken broth as needed - ¾ cup orzo pasta  - Bay leaves (optional) - Salt and pepper to taste Avgolemono Mixture: - 4 eggs - The juice of 2-3 lemons - lemon zesr - reserved broth from the Avgolemono Soup INSTRUCTIONS:  - Start by seasoning your chicken and searing it in a pot with a bit of oil until browned. Once golden, set the chicken aside for later. - In the same pot, sauté your vegetables until fragrant, then add Italian seasoning. add your chicken broth. - Return the chicken to the pot and set it to a gentle simmer for 45 minutes, or until tender. Once done, shred the chicken and add back to the soup. - Add the orzo pasta and let it cook in the broth for 8–10 minutes - Meanwhile, prepare the avgolemono mixture. In a separate bowl, whisk together eggs and add lemon juice/zest. To temper, pour in a thin stream a bit of hot soup while whisking constantly. This will prevent the eggs from scrambling. - Once tempered, gently stir the avgolemono mixture back into the pot. - Serve your soup hot, garnished with fresh dill/parsley and a drizzle of olive oil and enjoy! #Soups #asmr #ASMRCooking

Integrate your orzo pasta and top with a bay leaf and let simmer for a few minutes.  - After that add your meatballs in, remove the bayleaf and top with chopped spinach. video_name: Lamb in Apricot Sauce | Medieval Meals Ep. 12 This dish carries inspiration from the Silk Roads, where spices, fruits, and ideas flowed into Europe. Far from being isolated, medieval tables were shaped by trade routes that stretched across continents. Additionally for any depictions made of barbarians it’s important to note the popular image of wild raiders was just a fantasy. Barbarians in a traditional sense were skilled traders, craftsmen, and farmers — their lives far richer and more complex than the myths suggest. Disclaimer: While the content is inspired by real research from medieval times, the video incorporates elements of medieval faction and fiction for the purposes of entertainment. Researchers: - Igi Gomez Resources: - Adamson, M. W. (2004). Food in medieval times. Greenwood Press. - Hieatt, C. B., Butler, B., & Hosington, S. (1976). Pleyn delit: Medieval cookery for modern cooks. University of Toronto Press. INGREDIENTS:  - 2 lbs boneless lamb, in chunks - 1 lbs of lamb shanks, scored - Salt and pepper to taste - Oil or lard for frying - 1–2 onions, chopped - ⅓ cup of ground almonds - ½ lb dried apricots - Beef broth til pot is filled - 1 tsp ground ginger - 1 tsp ground coriander  INSTRUCTIONS:  - Start by scoring your lamb shanks and cutting your meat into bite sized cubes. Fry them in lard or oil until golden and set aside.  - In the same pot, saute onions until softened, and add ground almonds, apricots and beef stock. Season with ginger, coriander, pepper, and salt, and place in a heat-safe blender. Blend until thick. - Return the meat into the pot, and simmer for 20-30 minutes. Serve and enjoy! #medievalfood #darkfantasy #medieval #lightfantasy

video_name: Popcorn Chicken 🐓🍿 INGREDIENTS: Popcorn chicken: - 1kg of chicken thigh fillet, cubed - 2 tbsp of garlic powder - 2 tbsp hot sauce (here i’m using Cholula) - 2 tbsp old bay seasoning - 2 eggs - 1:1 ratio of rice and all purpose flour - Salt & pepper to taste - 1 cup of soaked tapioca pearls (soak for 1hr) Honey Mustard Dip: - 1 cup mayonnaise - ⅓ cup of mustard - ⅓ cup of honey - The juice of one lemon INSTRUCTIONS: - Start by slicing your chicken thighs into cubes, and adding them into a bowl. add two eggs, and season with garlic powder ,old bay, hot sauce, and worcestershire sauce. video_name: Este Pollo viene con Sorpresa Ingredientes: 1.5kg de Pollo (Pata y muslo) 2 Tazas de Harina de trigo 1/2 Taza de Fecula de maiz 2 Cucharaditas de Polvo de hornear Especias: (Podes poner lo que quieras) 2 Cucharadas de sal 1 Cucharada de Ajo en polvo 1 Cucharada de Pimenton 1 Cucharada de Tomillo 1 Cucharada de Pimienta 2 Huevos 100ml de Agua (Es medio a ojo) Para la salsa: Perejil 1/2 cebolla 1/2 diente de ajo 1 cebolla de verdeo 2 Cucharadas de Mayonesa 4 Cucharas de Yogur Neutro Sal y Pimienta Jugo de Medio limon Freir en aceite a 160°C 18 minutos y dejar enfriar. (Tarda en bajar la temperatura, asi que se sigue cocinando y se va poniendo mas crocante) Es importante que haya bastante aceite y no pongas mucho pollo porque sino lo vas a enfriar demasiado. Masomenos por 1lt de aceite mete 3/4 piezas Podes usar el truco de la cucharada de madera para medir la temperatura O si lo pones a fuego medio y precalentas por 15 minutos va estar bien. #fyp #recipesoftiktok #recetasfaciles #receta

video_name: Ramen Un par de aclaraciones previas.  El ramen es una comida que lleva tiempo, hay muchas versiones pero todas tienen como protagonistas caldos que llevan mucha coccion. Esta es una version rapida porque a mi tampoco me tienta la idea de estar 3 dias para hacer unos fideos. Ingredientes:  1kg de Cerdo (Usé Bondiola) Huevo duro Hongos (Usé champigniones, lo ideal es shitake pero no se consiguen facil) Fideos  Verdeo crudo picado Para el Caldo: Doras la carne 6 Dientes de Ajo 1 Jengibre 1 Cebolla de verdeo 1 Puerro 1 Cebolla 1/2 Taza de Azucar 1 Taza de Salsa de Soja Lo tapas con agua (Minimo 1,5 lt agrega) Dejas hervir a fuego bajo por 1 hora y media. Despues colas el caldo y metes lo hongos a remojar ahi mientras cortas la carne y preparas los fideos. Las cosas clave: Si el caldo te quedo muy fuerte (se redujo mucho) podes agregarle agua o al momento de servir en el plato una cucharada del agua de los fideos. Y si usaste el polvo saborizante que viene de los fideos ramen comprados todavia mejor. Para que los huevos queden así. Los pones al fuego con agua fria y en cuanto hierve con ganas contas 6 minutos exacto. Los sacas y rapido en agua helada. La idea de atar la carne es para que no pierda la forma circular. #receta #recetasfaciles #recipesoftiktok #fyp

video_name: Asi es El Verdadero Goulash Ingredientes para 4: 1kg de Carne  2 Cebollas  4 Cucharadas de Paprika 1 Cucharada de Semillas de Kummel 1/2 Morron 1 Tomate 800gr de Papa Caldo/agua y Sal Para lo Csipetke: 1 huevo 200gr de Harina Sal Haces la masa, la pellizcas y los tiras 5 minutos a cocinar Claves: Es importante ir mirando el goulash para que no se quede sin agua. Born in the mountains where myths and reality blur, he’s the descendant of ancient guardian hounds said to protect villages from spirits. Some even whisper his ancestors roamed battlefields alongside warriors, larger than life and feared by all. Now, raised by his human, this colossal companion isn’t just a pet, he’s a guardian, a friend, and a reminder that sometimes legends walk among us… on four paws. #GiantDog #Dog #DogTraining #Pets #Animals

video_name: nutella stuffed chocolate chip cookies !    recipe:   1/2 cup butter, browned (113g) 1/4 cup granulated sugar (50g) 1/2 cup dark brown sugar, packed (100g) 1 large egg  1 tsp vanilla extract (5g) 1 1/2 cups all-purpose flour (190g) 1/2 tsp baking soda (3g) 1/4 tsp salt (1g) chocolate chips(measure with your heart idk, i used @Nestle Toll House ) 6 tbsp nutella(90g)(i used 3 for the cookies & the rest to drizzle.)  instructions- brown the butter & let cool slightly. in a bowl whisk together the browned butter & sugars until glossy. add the egg & vanilla and mix until combined. add in the flour, baking soda, and salt and fold gently then add chocolate chips and fold until the dough comes together. scoop dough balls, flatten slightly, place a frozen nutella scoop in the center, and roll it back up. bake at 350°f (175°c) for 11–13 minutes until golden on the edges but soft in the middle.( i made 3 big cookies & 6 small ones. the bigger ones cooked for 15-17 minutes. )    #nutella #chocolatechipcookies #cookies #fyp #baking

video_name: salted caramel brownies !! also thank you sm for 200k 💞      here’s the recipe:   1/2 cup brown butter(113g) 1/2 cup granulated sugar(100g) 1/2 cup brown sugar(100g) 2 eggs 1/2 tsp vanilla(2g) 1/2 cup flour(60g) 1/2 cup cocoa powder(45g) 1/2 cup choc chips(85g)( split to add some in batter and some in butter )( i used dark choc if you use semi or milk your brownies will be sweeter so i reccomend adjusting the sugar 2-3 tbsp. )( i used @Nestle Toll House )  1/4 tsp salt(1.5g) 1/4 tsp baking soda(1g) 1 tsp instant coffee ( i used @NESCAFÉ USA ) brown your butter and add in the chocolate chips while it’s still warm. melt the chocolate and add in both sugars. ( make sure it’s still warm to melt it a bit ) mix well then add in your eggs. mix until it gets thick & glossy. sift in your dry ingredients & chocolate chips and fold everything together. bake at 350•F for about 25 minutes. let it cool and then drizzle caramel.    quick & easy salted caramel recipe:   1/2 cup brown sugar(100g) 1/4 cup butter(56g) 1/4 cup heavy cream(60g)  1/4 tsp salt ( adjust to taste )(3g)   add your sugar & butter to a pan and let it melt continue to mix so it doesn’t burn. once it’s bubbling slowly add in heavy cream, it’ll bubble a bit but keep mixing. take it off heat and add salt then let it cool.  #brownie #recipe #baking #fyp #fudgybrownies

video_name: s’more chocolate chip cookies !! ik i said i was done but i love making these videos😅    here’s the recipe :   1/2 cup brown butter (113g) 1/4 cup granulated sugar (50g) 1/2 cup dark brown sugar, (100g) 1 large egg  1 tsp vanilla extract (5g) 1 1/2 cups all-purpose flour (190g) 1/2 tsp baking soda (3g) 1/4 tsp salt (1g) chocolate chips(measure with your heart idk, i used @Nestle Toll House choc chips also hersheys for the top & middle ) @jetpuffed marshmallows ( i used the jumbo ones :D ) & @Honey Maid graham crackers.  instructions- brown the butter & let cool slightly. in a bowl whisk together the browned butter & sugars until glossy. add the egg & vanilla and mix until combined. add in the flour, baking soda, and salt and fold gently then add chocolate chips and fold until the dough comes together. scoop dough balls, flatten slightly, place over your graham cracker & chocolate and form the dough around the marshmallow. ( i reccomend cutting the mallow in half if you’re doing smaller cookies) bake at 350°f for 11–13 minutes until golden on the edges.( i made 3 big cookies & 8 small ones. the bigger ones cooked for 15-17 minutes. )   #smores #cookies #baking #fyp #chocolatechipcookies

video_name: chocolate nutella cinnamon rolls 🤎 these tasted like chocolate donuts ??    recipe:   3/4 cup warm milk(180g) 3 tbsp melted butter(43g) 4 tbsp granulated sugar(50g) 2 1/4 tsp yeast(7g) 1 egg 1 yolk 3 cups of flour(360g) 3 tbsp cocoa powder(18g) 1/4 tsp salt(1.5g) 1/4 cup heavy cream(60g) ( goes on top before baking )    mix your warm milk. sugar, and yeast and let sit for 5-10 minutes. once frothy add in your egg and butter and mix. then add in your dry ingredients and continue mixing until it becomes a shaggy dough. knead until a smooth dough forms. ( you may need to add a bit more flour. but i reccomend coating your hands in olive oil and kneading that way. ) let sit in an oiled bowl covered for 1 hr. after the hour punch the dough down and roll it out.    filling:   1/4 cup melted butter(57g)  1 cup brown sugar(200g) 3 tsp cinnamon(7-8g) 2-3 tbsp nutella (40-60g) 1 tbsp cocoa powder(6g)   mix until combined. let your butter cool a tad bit just so it doesn’t melt the sugar. spread over rolled out dough & roll them up. cut your desired cinnamon roll sizes & let sit for another 30 minutes. pour heavy cream over top of rolls and bake at 350•F for about 25-35 minutes. ( can vary depending on your oven ) while they’re still warm spread nutella over top. or use a different frosting recipe( i didn’t like the idea of chocolate cream cheese frosting idk )    #chocolate #cinnamonroll #nutella #bakingrecipe #fyp

video_name: crispy cheesy garlic potato balls!! this time they’re super crispy :D    easy recipe:   5 yellow potatoes 5 tbsp cornstarch (plus some for rolling) (40g) 1 tsp salt (adjust to taste) (6g) 1 tsp garlic powder (3g) 1/2 tsp onion powder (1.5g) 1/4 tsp black pepper (0.5g) 1 tsp parsley (1g)   cut & peel your potatoes. then boil until they’re fork tender. add to a bowl and mash up until smooth. then add in your spices & cornstarch, mix until a dough forms. seperate your dough ( i did 1 heaping tbsp for each, i got 9 balls ) then flatten & add your cheese. roll them back up and roll in cornstarch( don’t skip this step, you want to lightly coat them it helps with the crispy skin ). let freeze for 30 mins - 1 hr. then fry until golden brown on each side. let dry on a rack a bit before eating.    #cheese #garlic #potatoes #Recipe #baking

video_name: carrot cake!! 🤎      easy recipe:   1 cup brown butter (225g) 1 cup granulated sugar (200g) 1/2 cup brown sugar (100g) 4 eggs 1/2 cup of buttermilk ( if you don’t have it mix 1 cup regular milk with 1 tbsp lemon juice or vinegar) 2 tsp vanilla 2 cups grated carrots 2 cups of flour (250g) 1 1/2 tsp baking powder(6g) 1 tsp baking soda (5g) 1 1/2 tsp cinnamon(3g) 1/2 tsp nutmeg (1g) 1/2 tsp salt(3g) preheat your oven to 350•F. whisk together the dry ingredients in one bowl. in another, mix the sugars, butter, eggs, and vanilla until smooth. combine the wet and dry, then fold in grated carrots. i made two 8x8 cakes with this recipe.    bake for 25-35 minutes. let cool before assembling the cake !    brown butter cream cheese frosting recipe:   1/2 cup butter(113g) 8 oz softened cream cheese(225g) 2 1/2 cups powdered sugar(300g) 1 1/2 tsp vanilla 1 tsp cinnamon 2 tsp maple syrup  pinch of salt    brown your butter and let it cool completely, then whip it up until fluffy beat in the cream cheese, vanilla, maple syrup & the spices. let cool until you’re ready to use .    #brownbutter #carrotcake #recipe #baking #fyp

video_name: the best classic fluffy & soft banana bread. i think plain banana bread is growing on me idk    recipe:   3 bananas 1/2 cup melted butter(113g) 1/2 cup white sugar(100g) 1/4 cup brown sugar(50g) 2 eggs, room temp 1 tsp vanilla paste  1/3 cup greek yogurt(80g) 1 3/4 cup flour(220g) 1 tsp baking powder 1/2 tsp baking soda  1/4 tsp salt  1 tsp cinnamon ( optional )   mash your bananas and mix in your melted butter, add in your sugars & mix. add eggs, vanilla, yogurt & mix until combined. fold in your dry ingredients (don’t overmix). bake at 350•F for 55-65 minutes. ( mine took longer bc of my pan ). let cool before slicing and enjoy :)    #bananabread #recipe #baking #fyp

video_name: happy october 1st 🍁 !! pumpkin pie cookies, crumbl dupeee??   recipe: yields about 10 cookies.    1/2 cup softened butter(113g) 1/2 cup granulated sugar(100g) 1/4 cup brown sugar(50g) 1 egg yolk 1/2 tsp vanilla paste(2g) 1 1/4 cup flour(156g) 1/4 tsp salt(1.5g) 1/4 tsp baking powder(1g) 1 tbsp milk(15g)   mix your butter & sugars until combined, then add your egg & vanilla, mix and fold in your dry ingredients ( i added milk to mine because i felt the dough was a bit too dry, if you’re looking for a more puffy cookie, don’t add the milk & add 1/2 tsp baking powder instead of 1/4. ) seperate your dough balls ( i did about 1 heaping tbsp for each cookie ) and place on a baking sheet( i tried shaping mine but it did not stay after baking LOL ) bake at 350•F for about 11-12 minutes ( depending on how big your cookies are ) bake until the edges are set but the middle is slightly soft. after you take them out, while they’re still warm, shape them (optional). let cool and add filling !    pumpkin filling:   8 oz cream cheese 1/2 cup pumpkin puree 4 tbsp brown sugar 1 tsp pumpkin pie spice ( or 1/2 tsp nutmeg, 1/8 tsp all spice, & ginger ) 1 tsp cinnamon   place the pumpkin puree in a clean piece of cheesecloth, gently squeeze to remove excess liquid. repeat until the pumpkin feels thick & not watery, ( you can add more pumpkin to taste ). add to bowl with cream cheese & other spices & mix until fluffy & combined. set aside until your ready to use ( refrigerate )   homemade whipped cream:   1 cup heavy whipping cream(240g) 2-3 tbsp powdered sugar(15-30g)(adjust to taste) 1 tsp vanilla (5g)   whip until stiff peaks form and pipe over cookies!   #pumpkinpie #cookies #fallbaking #october #fyp

video_name: Maybe you can help me think this through? When I started six years ago, I planned to hire a chef who could bring my ideas to life better than I could. I’d run the floor and manage the service side, which is also my area of strength. The bigger vision was to expand quickly and eventually open a brunch café–bakery concept. But fast forward to now, and things have considerably changed. I don’t see myself necessarily doing a brunch spot anymore and gruelling away on scrambled eggs 7 days a week or leading service (at least not right away). If anything now, I see myself more than ever in the kitchen instead. There are obvious trade-offs. It could slow down my growth with the initial launch, and I might not be as visible as I originally planned. But if I prove myself in the kitchen and do it well, it solidifies my credibility beyond just “playing” with fruits and with flashy edits to, a perhaps, legitimate, skilled chef. So, as I begin to double down more on my future vision, I’ve been increasingly torn about where to focus now, whether to begin with pastry or a restaurant concept, and which one should become the flagship aka driving force that sets the tone for everything to come. Pastry, brunch, cafe, bakery fine dining, pub... what do you see first?

video_name: HELADITOS DE BANANA, COCO Y CHOCOLATE: la combinación que nunca falla 🍌🍫 • Una receta simple y fresca, perfecta para tener lista en el freezer. video_name: SALCHICHAS DE MIL FORMAS: una más rica que la otra 🌭🔥 . Tenía ganas de probar algunas recetas fáciles con salchichas y terminé haciendo tres en un solo video 🙃 Quedaron re distintas entre sí, pero todas perfectas para una picada con una vueltita más linda ✨ . La intensidad justa que combina con todo 💥 . 👩🏼‍🍳 INGREDIENTES: Pancakes de salchicha  • 150 g de harina de trigo  • 40 g de azúcar  • 1 cda de polvo de hornear  • 1 huevo 🥚  • 120 ml de leche 🥛  • Salchichas cortadas en rodajas 🌭 Palmechichas picantes  • Masa de tarta hojaldrada 🥐  • Salchichas  • Ketchup  • Queso en hebras 🧀  • Huevo (para pincelar)  • @Takis Argentina triturados 🔥 Brochette de salchichas rebozadas  • Salchichas  • Harina 🌾  • Huevo 🥚  • Pan rallado 🍞  •  Perfectas para una juntada o para salir del paso con algo distinto. ¡Guardalo y probalas cuando quieras! 💫 • #recetas #salchicha #cheese #takis

video_name: TAMAGO SANDO Y ATÚN SANDO: un clásico japonés, fácil y rápido 🥪✨ •  Tenía muchas ganas de probar estos sando al estilo japonés para salir un poco de los sándwiches de siempre. Allá son re clásicos, los venden en estaciones y kioscos, pero bueno… como estamos medio lejos, los hice en casa y quedaron buenísimos. 🙌🏼 •  ✨ Tip: para el tamago, separé las claras de las yemas cuando ya estaban cocidas. Hice un puré con las yemas y piqué las claras bien chiquitas antes de mezclar con la mayo y la crema. Queda mucho más parejo y cremoso, se integra mejor con el pan y posta vale la pena tomarse ese ratito. • 👩🏼‍🍳 INGREDIENTES: Tamago Sando (huevo): • 8 huevos 🥚 • Mayonesa Natura 🥄 • Ciboulette 🌿 • Crema 🥛 • Sal 🧂 • Pimienta 🌶️ • Atún Sando: • 2 latas de atún 🐟 • Mayonesa Natura 🥄 • 1 tomate 🍅 • 1 palta 🥑 • 1/2 cebolla morada 🧅 • 30 ml de crema 🥛 • Para los dos: • Pan bien suave 🍞 • Quedan muy buenos así que vale la pena probarlos... ¡Contame cuál te animás a hacer! 😍✨ • #recetas #sandwich #japan

video_name: SUSHI BAKE i was lying bout the 6 7 billion views😄 6 7 is trending right now lmaoo SALMON MIXTURE 2 salmon filets ½ imitation crab 5 oz cream cheese, soften preferred 1/3 cup Japanese mayo 2 TBSP sirarcha 3-4 sheets of seaweed RICE 3 cups cooked white rice 1 tsp mirin 1 tsp rice vinegar Salt to taste TO SERVE: seaweed avocado cucumbers jalpenos 1. Season your salmon filets with: salt, black pepper, paprika and olive oil. Cook using your preferred method… airfryer, stovetop or oven. I air fried mine at 400F for 12 minutes. 2. Shred your imitation crab and then cut smaller so the strips aren’t too long. 3. By now, your salmon should be done cooking. Add your cooked salmon you’re your shredded imitation crab.  Break the salmon apart. If there is skin on you salmon, then discard. 4. Add 5 oz soften cream cheese, 1/3 cup cream cheese and 2 TBSP sirarcha. Combine this well, set this aside. 5. In a baking dish (mine is 9x13), add 3 cups of cooked white rice. Season rice with: 1 tsp mirin, 1 tsp rice vinegar and salt to taste. Combine this well then flatten the rice into the baking dish. 6. Next, top your rice with shredded seaweed or furikake. 7. Add an even layer of salmon mixture on top your rice + seaweed. Bake at 380F for 10 minutes, then broil for 3-5 minutes. 8. Drizzle some siracha and spicy mayo on top of your sushi bake. Garnish with chopped scallion and black sesame seeds. 9. Serve with seaweed and other toppings like jalapenos, cucumbers and/ or avocados.

Wash throughly and place into a large enough air tight container (note: musard greens are very dirty so make sure you wash it several times) 2. In a mixing bowl, combine: water, sugar, vinegar and salt. Mix until sugar is dissolved and then pour this mixture over your mustard greens. Let this sit at room temp for 2 days then move into the fridge for at least 1 week before enjoying.

video_name: STOVE TOP BO KHO Recipe is from my bestie @Tracey Le | JustlikeMoms    BEEF MARINADE 2-3 lb chuck roast 3 TBSP minced garlic 1 TBSP chicken bouillon ½ TBSP salt 1 TBSP fish sauce 3 TBSP hoisin sauce 1 oz bo kho/ beef stew seasoning* *1 bag of bo kho seasoning is 2 oz so you need 1 oz. You will use the other half later   BEEF STEW 3 TBSP minced garlic 1  oz bo kho seasoning 1/3 cup @heinz tomato ketchup 2 TBSP hoisin sauce 8 stalks of lemongrass 2 cans chicken stock (14.5 oz each can) 1 can coco rico/ coconut soda (12 oz each can) 3 cups hot water 1 yellow or white onion, cut into large chunks   ADDITIONAL INGREDIENTS 5 carrots, skinned and cut 1 inch Oil, for cooking Cornstarch slurry (3 TBSP cornstarch + 3 TBSP water)   FOR SERVING: Noodles (I used rice noodles/ pho noodles0 French baguette/ crusty bread/ French roll Rice Chopped scallion Chopped cilantro Thinly sliced onions   INSTRUCTIONS 1.        Cut chuck roast into large pieces.   2.        Make your marinade by combining all of the ingredients listed under BEEF MARINADE. Marinate your beef for at least 2 hours.   3.        Prepare your lemongrass: cut off the leafy ends of your lemongrass and discard the leafy end. With the remainder of ur lemongrass, peel the first couple outer layer of your lemongrass and cut a piece piece of the root end off. Then using a mallet or spine of your knife, gently bruise your lemongrass. Cut lemongrass into 3-4 in wide pieces. Set this aside.   4.        In a pot, heat up some oil and saute 3 TBSP garlic until fragrant.   5.        Next add the rest of your bo kho season (1 oz), 1/3 cup Heinz ketchup and 2 TBSP hoisin sauce. Combine well.   6.        Next, add your prepared lemongrass and cook for a couple of minutes.   7.        Add marinated beef and cook for ~5 minutes.   8.        Then add 2 cans of chicken broth, 1 can coco rico and 3 cups hot water, and 1 yellow or white onion. Bring this to a boil and then reduce heat, cover and simmer for at least 1.5 hours. I let mine simmer for 2.5 hours. During the simmering process, you will get foam that floats to the top, skim the foam out.   9.        After you are done simmering, add carrots and cook for another 10 minutes or until your carrots are fork tender.   10.  Thicken your beef stew by cranking heat to high and adding a slurry (3 TBSP cornstarch + 3 TBSP water). Leave this to cook for 3-5 minutes.. ur stew will slightly thicken.   11.  Now assemble a bowl.  I like to eat my beef stew with pho noodles. If u prefer to eat with bread, you can do that as well. Assemble a bowl with: pho noodles, stew, chopped scallion, chopped cilantro, thinly sliced onions, lime juice and/or chili oil.

video_name: CANH CHUA – SOUR SOUP   Kimchi Jiggae translates to kimchi soup. Canh chua translates to “sour soup”. Canh = soup. Chua = sour.   1 lb pork riblets 8-9 cups water ½ large yellow onion ~5 cups pickled mustard greens 3 TBSP mushroom seasoning 1 tsp tamarind powder 2 tsp salt 1.5 TBSP rock sugar 2 roma tomatoes Hand full chopped scallion   1.        Par boil riblets for 5 minutes and then rinse and drain under cold water. 2.        In a pot, add your parboiled pork riblets, ½ large onion, and 8-9 cups of water and bring to a boil. Once boiling, cover and reduce heat to simmer. Simmer for 25 minutes. At the 15-minute mark, re fill water if needed (because some water will evaporate) 3.        After 25 minutes of simmering, remove your onion. Add pickled mustard greens and season with: 3 TBSP mushroom seasoning, 1 tsp tamarind powder, 2 tsp salt, and 2 TBSP rock sugar. Bring this back to a boil 4.        Add tomatoes wedges and chopped scallion. Immediately turn off heat.

video_name: Transformar una cocina sin obras y sin gastar demasiado es posible ✨ En este vídeo os enseño cómo hemos lacado las puertas y frentes de los muebles con un resultado limpio, luminoso y actual. Es el mismo proceso que podéis aplicar también en puertas de paso o en otros muebles. 📋 Materiales y herramientas: Lijas grano 180 y taco de lijado Masilla reparadora de madera Sellador de madera blanca (para filos si hace falta) Cinta de carrocero y plásticos para proteger Imprimación al agua para madera Esmalte/laca al agua acabado satinado Barniz transparente protector Rodillos de espuma/acabado fino Brocha para esquinas y detalles Guantes de protección 💡 Trucos que me ayudan a un mejor resultado ✔️ Numerar puertas y herrajes antes de desmontar → el montaje final es mucho más fácil. ✔️ Tapar con masilla huecos e imperfecciones antes de empezar → acabado más uniforme. ✔️ Aplicar capas finas y uniformes con rodillo → evita marcas y da mejor resultado. ✔️ Respetar los tiempos de secado → clave para un acabado duradero. Y atentos, porque muy pronto veréis cómo aplico estas mismas bases low cost y sin obra en el lavadero, y también os enseñaré el rincón del desayunador 🌿 . . . #DIY #ReformaSinObra #CocinaLowCost #Lacado #Interiorismo

video_name: Pesawat kecil seperti Cessna atau Piper menggunakan bahan bakar khusus yang disebut AVGAS 100LL (Aviation Gasoline). Angka ‘100’ menunjukkan angka oktan yang sangat tinggi, artinya bahan bakar ini mampu menahan panas dan tekanan tinggi tanpa menyebabkan knocking (ledakan dini di mesin). Kenapa harus begitu? Mesin pesawat saat take-off dan climb bekerja pada putaran tinggi dan beban maksimum. Kalau diisi dengan bensin mobil biasa seperti Pertalite (oktan 90), mesin bisa mengalami knocking parah, tenaga turun, getaran berlebih, suhu cepat naik, hingga berisiko merusak mesin. Analoginya seperti motor sport 250cc yang dipaksa minum bensin oktan rendah. Memang bisa jalan, tapi performa berkurang, mesin cepat panas, dan umur komponen lebih pendek. Bedanya, kalau motor mogok bisa berhenti di pinggir jalan, sedangkan pesawat harus tetap aman di udara. Karena itu, pemilihan bahan bakar bukan sekadar pilihan, tapi soal keselamatan penerbangan.

video_name: Pesawat latih Piper Warrior menggunakan mesin andalan Pabrikan Lycoming O-320-D3G, mesin piston 4 silinder berpendingin udara. Walaupun kapasitasnya ‘hanya’ sekitar 160 tenaga kuda, mesin ini terkenal bandel, sederhana, dan mudah dirawat, cocok untuk pesawat latih yang dipakai sehari-hari. Mesin ini bisa dibilang ‘partner belajar’ yang sabar. Tahan dipakai untuk take-off pendek, touch-and-go berulang kali, hingga latihan stall dan manuver dasar. Justru karena ketangguhannya, banyak sekolah pilot di seluruh dunia menjadikan Piper Warrior sebagai kuda kerja mereka. Kalau mau dianalogikan, Lycoming O-320 itu seperti mesin motor touring 4-tak yang tahan banting. Bukan yang paling kencang, tapi bisa diajak jalan jauh, tangguh di berbagai kondisi, dan jarang rewel kalau dirawat benar. Bedanya, motor touring kalau mogok tinggal minggir, sedangkan Piper Warrior harus tetap terbang dengan aman. Itulah kenapa mesin ini dirancang simpel, teruji, dan bisa diandalkan. Btw @ppicurug.official @penerbangppic punya 2 tipe pesawat latih Single Engine, yakni Piper Warrior III dan Piper Archer III Garmin 1000, nice banget kan 👌🏻

bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: Since so many thought I blocked the vents with the @ragofabrication dash mount I figured may as well block the controls for them too hahahaha • I got this @midlandradio two way radio and figured this would give it a good place to mount as well as other stuff • The instructions said to pull apart the console but I used Rivnuts instead and it worked perfect. I didn’t have to pull anything apart • I don’t know about you but I loose Allen keys the week I get them, I’ve had this @gearwrenchtools T-handle set for years now and haven’t lost any of them. I feel like the labeled rack being on this tool chest keeps me inline • These @ragofabrication are available @4Runner Lifestyle

bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: Added this @Kimpex USA front and back windshield to the Maverick • This was a massive upgrade that took no time to install. The wind that goes through the cab is insane, it pulls on the helmets and there is no way to talk to each other • It’s made of 1/4” polycarbonate which is 250x stronger than glass and 25x stronger than acrylic. The reason I wanted this over glass is because I pull it on my flat deck and don’t want to crack the glass • I’ve sure been using this 1/4” @gearwrenchtools torque wrench a lot lately. It definitely fills the void that the 1/2” and 3/8” can’t get down to. Comes with a nice case as well  . . . #tools #kimpex #gearwrench #canam #maverickx3turborr

bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: On our journey @Overland Expo we met @Slouch Couch  • This really got my interest because room can be tight when packing for an adventure but having a loveseat on hand would be so cool • So here’s the info It has a built in USB C rechargeable inflator/deflator. It inflates in 90 seconds. The material is 500D nylon condura so it can take a beating • The storage bag is way bigger than the couch so it’s super easy to get back in • They have it on their website right now $70 off making it $280 • It’s definitely become the favorite place to sit when we are out . . . #tools #camping #couch #furniture #slouchcouch

bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: If you have installed a lot of rivets by hand you can definitely appreciate this tool • This Hilti Rivet tool runs on their Nuron battery platform. All you have to do is press the trigger and it does the rest. It keeps things consistent. • It has a spot for the different size nose pieces and has a container to catch the mandrel @Hilti North America  . . . #tools #construction #hiltipartner #hilti #hiltitools

bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: Gotta make sure you do the right prep work!! • I’m going to coat this floor and ramp but before that I need to sand down this floor and vacuum it many times to make sure the product will adhere properly • I decided to go with this 5” Bosch sander. No cord and I ran it with the bag • I went over this floor twice sanding it for over 30 min straight. I ran the 4ah core battery and by the end it was still showing 2 out of 5 bars • I had to empty the bag 3 times as well. It worked really good • Next I’ll put a few coats down on the floor. They use 3/4 plywood for the floor in the @Southland Trailer Corp.  @Bosch Power Tools  . . . #tools #construction #boschpartner #boschtools #construction

bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: I never thought I’d be moving around my @Southland Trailers cargo trailer with a Makita drill • With the @Trailer Valet it’s possible! • I saw this like 5 years ago at a trade show and figured it would be handy! Wait till you see what I do with it next. @Makita Tools USA @Makita Canada Inc.  . . . #tools #construction #trailervalet #makita #makitatools

bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: Where you live are you using clipped head or full round head nails in your nailer? • Here we use clipped, it’s actually pretty hard to find a box of full round in stores here. Sorta a special order thing • This is the @FLEXPOWERTOOLSNA framing nailer. I pulled it straight outta the box and took it right to this saturated pressure treated 6x6. • I got 3-1/4” nails in it and set it to full depth. I’ve used pretty much every battery powered framing nailer on the market and I’m sure you will agree that the faster you go the chance or a proud nail is way higher • I was surprised to see that it was the opposite with this, it was straight up burning the nails even further with speed. I do think I could have even pushed it faster • This will be the nailer that goes in my tool trailer build so you’ll see more of it soon . . . #tools #construction #framing #carpentry #flexpartner

bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: Makita has just announced New 18v nailers! • Here is the angled 16g It can take 1-1/4 to 2-1/2 • So let’s toss in a compact battery and some 2-1/2 nails and see how it does • First some spruce with ease, I found some maple cutoffs and left in the 2-1/2. Now it is a full depth and as you can see it had no problem and even at that speed it kept them sinking at a consistent depth • Now bump fire isn’t normally something you use on a nailer like this but it does show the power of it, especially with that small battery • It has a light, a couple extra nose adapters and belt clip. Oh and it’s made in Japan @Makita Tools USA  . . . #tools #construction #makita #makitatools #makitapartner

bio:
Найди наш магазин на Wildberries или Ozon
по названию бренда Bull Stickers
video_name: Артикул на ✅Wildberries #251909820  Монашка с открытым ртом WB #247247625 Монашка с пальцами у виска WB #260427148 Наклейки на стойки дверей авто - это стильное и практичное решение для вашего автомобиля. Изготовлены из прочной виниловой пленки с матовой ламинацией, которая обеспечивает долговечность и устойчивость к внешним воздействиям. Размер подходит для большинства моделей автомобилей. В комплекте 2 штуки, что позволяет оформить обе стороны. Они легко наносятся самостоятельно, обрезаются по размеру детали, а подробная инструкция входит в комплект. После удаления не оставляют следов и не повреждают поверхность. Срок эксплуатации составляет до 18 месяцев, устойчивы к мойке, не выгорают на солнце, сохраняют яркость, не царапаются. bio: I'm journalist & motorcycle reviewer @otomotif_tv @otomotifweekly_ @gridoto.com
video_name: CUSTOMAXi 2025 seri pertama pecah banget! Berlangsung di Queen City Mall, Semarang, Jawa Tengah akhir pekan lalu (20-21 September 2025), totalnya ada 80 motor ikut adu keren konsep modifikasi.  Ada di video kali ini, kita lihat beberapa modifikasi yang keren-keren! Dari 2 kelas utama yaitu STREET MAXi dan SUPER MAXi. untuk masing-masing tipe motor mulai dari XMAX, NMAX, AEROX sampai LEXi. Bukan hanya kontes modifikasi, ada juga beberapa keseruan lainnya, seperti tatto temporary, photobooth AI, sampai live painting. Minggu ini, CUSTOMAXi 2025 giliran menyambangi Makassar, Sulawesi Selatan sebagai kota kedua. Minggu, 28 September 2025 bertempat di Mari Arcade, Mall Ratu Indah. Jangan sampai enggak dateng ya! #customaxi #customaxi2025 #yamahalexi #xmax #aerox #aeroxmodifikasi #aerox155 #nmax #nmaxmodifikasi

bio: I'm journalist & motorcycle reviewer @otomotif_tv @otomotifweekly_ @gridoto.com
video_name: Gak tau motor siapa hehe.. Tag ya kalau ada yang tahu ownernya. Kedua Honda NSR250R MC28 ini jadi salah satu magnet yang bikin langkah pengunjung berhenti di IMOS 2025.  Honda NSR250 MC28 ini masuk kategori racing replica dan dirilis pertama kali pada Oktober 1993. Pakai mesin 2-tak V-twin 249cc powernya 40 hp, transmisi 6 percepatan, dan sudah pakai fitur RC Valve. Salah satu fitur paling keren di zamannya adalah PGM Memory Card berfungsi sebagai microchip dengan engine mapping berbeda. Powernya bisa naik dari 40 hp ke 65 hp. Gokils.  Btw, yang merah sudah upgrade kaki-kaki pakai USD dan upgrade rem. Cakep ya! #nsr #nsr250 #nsr250r #nsr150 #hondansr

video_name: On 5 December 2012, at around 19:15 local time, the Baltic Ace, en route from Zeebrugge to Kotka with a cargo of 1,417 cars (mainly Mitsubishi from Japanese and Thai factories), collided with the Cypriot container ship Corvus J 65 nautical miles off the province of Zealand. The ship was holed and quickly sank. The container ship Corvus J remained afloat and took on board survivors from the sunken ship. bio: I write songs 👋
video_name: A song about some of the heavier things I’ve been feeling in postpartum. I felt mom guilt even writing this one, but I’ve been posting a lot of super happy content on here …So here’s a little reminder that social media doesn’t tell the full truth. Being her mom is the greatest thing I’ll ever do. I prayed for it. I also haven’t left the house alone in 4 months. Motherhood is not all sunshine and rainbows. Sometimes it’s a scary, lonely, confusing, transformative, existential rollercoaster.  I’m gonna call this one “The Death of Her Old Self”  ✍️

bio: For 40+ years, we've been pioneering voice for the LGBTQ+ community🏳️‍🌈 🏳️‍⚧️
video_name: 🎤 Tonight’s the night. Join us for Unapologetic: Our Celebration of Queer Black Love — a powerful Juneteenth concert honoring Black queer joy, resilience, and artistry. Featuring performances by our Black-identifying singers and special guests  Shea Diamond, Kizha Carr, and speaker Ricky Day, this evening uplifts stories at the intersection of Blackness and queerness with soul, strength, and song. Presented in proud partnership with our Black affinity group, Melanated, this event is a celebration of freedom, identity, and community. 🗓 Tonight at 8 PM 📍 Cathedral of St. John the Divine 🎟 Contact the box office to get on the waitlist! #Juneteenth #QueerBlackLove #BlackQueerJoy #MelanatedVoices #NYCGMC #SheaDiamond #KizhaCarr #RickyDay #Unapologetic #NYCPride #BlackLGBTQ #FreedomAndJoy #CelebratePride #CathedralConcert #FreeEvent

video_name: Things I find helpful when I realize I’m falling into depression: — noticing when you’re starting to fall into depression is a huge  first step to getting out of it or avoiding falling into it any further. It gives you a chance to “interrupt” the cycle before it takes over. -Finding structure can be difficult but it’s extremely helpful. Starting small is usually best.  Example can be- *Set a time to go to bed or to wake up in the morning  *give yourself 3 small tasks to complete (can be as simple as drink a glass of water or sit outside) *Eating something every few hours even if it’s small.  -Moving our body’s are super important. It doesn’t need to be a full work out. It could be stretching, going on a 5 minute walk, wiggling our toes, etc.  Movement can disrupt the emotional freeze that comes with early depression. -Grounding yourself through your senses can be extremely effective.  You can run cold or warm water over your hands, light a candle or smell essential oil, listen to a favorite song and focus on just one instrument, etc  This brings your nervous system into the present moment  -One thing I’ve found difficult but possibly the most helpful is reaching out to someone close. You don’t have to get super deep into it but saying something as simple as “I’m not feeling great and I just want to acknowledge that” is more than enough.  Most people want to be there they just don’t know when to be.  -Return to what reminds You of You maybe that’s painting, or playing a sport, or dancing, or writing, or reading, or listening to a playlist you made, etc. Whatever feels like You.   Remind Yourself: This Is a Season, Not a Sentence #Art #artist

video_name: Entrenamiento en el Centro de Alto Rendimiento K9 Pasión ✨ Una jornada intensa, trabajando con personas estáticas y mucha estimulación, con varios perros al mismo tiempo en el mismo ejercicio. 🐕💪 Los guías y sus compañeros de cuatro patas tuvieron que estar 100% conectados, atentos a cada detalle, ya que había un perro un poco reactivo. 🔥 💯 El resultado fue muy satisfactorio: logramos mantener la concentración, superar los retos y seguir avanzando. 📈 Seguimos sumando experiencias, aprendizajes y momentos únicos con nuestro equipo canino. 🐾 Feliz de ver cómo evolucionamos día a día. #EntrenamientoCanino #PerrosDetectores #CentroK9 #Obediencia #PerrosDeTrabajo

video_name: Ya podemos anunciar que con Vora he conseguido dar un gran paso: conocerla de verdad, conectar con ella y comenzar a bailar juntos. Despacio, porque aún quedan procesos importantes como cambios de escenarios y nuevas estimulaciones, pero ya tenemos un vínculo que antes no existía. Empezamos a cabalgar juntos. Estoy feliz, aunque consciente de que queda mucho trabajo: mejorar la marca, ganar más confianza y seguir creciendo. Pero el cambio que hemos logrado es espectacular. Semper Fidelis. K9 Pasión. #k9 #UnidadCanina #PerrosPolicía #k9policia #malinois

bio:
K9 policía / Traning K9,
detección deportiva, 
obediència bàsica, 
Acadèmia K9
video_name: Al mirar atrás y ver el camino recorrido con Vora, me doy cuenta de lo mucho que hemos avanzado juntos. Lo que en un principio parecía un reto enorme —que se concentrara, que dejara a un lado los impulsos y se enfocara en el juguete— hoy ya es una realidad. Y eso, aunque parezca un detalle, para mí significa muchísimo. Con la guía de Manel, poco a poco vamos subiendo escalones, buscando una evidencia cada vez más sólida, más limpia, más fina. Sé que todavía queda un largo camino, que el verdadero alto nivel está lejos, pero cada pequeño logro me recuerda que lo importante no es llegar rápido, sino avanzar. Lo más valioso de todo este proceso no es solo ver a Boran crecer, sino también lo que me enseña a mí: paciencia, constancia y confianza en el trabajo bien hecho. Al final, este viaje se resume en eso… avanzar, avanzar y avanzar. #k9 #UnidadCanina #PerrosPolicía #k9policia #malinois

video_name: If u have an impulse to get a cat…. Take this as a sign because I met george at an animal welfare league adoption center when I was 19 yrs old and visited a mall. Was not planning on getting a cat at all but saw 3 month old george and got the impression he was perfect and amazing. I left without him but kept thinking about him, walking around the mall thinking maybe I should go back. I decided to go back and asked for a sign if I should really impulsively adopt a kitten. When I went back someone else was saying goodbye to him, deciding not to adopt him. I took that as my sign and paid $50 for a fully neutered, vaxxed and microchipped kitren, shocked that they let me take him home as a 19 yr old college student. It shows you how many cats need homes that i was deemed good enough. I Never expected him to become an actual keyboard cat but here we are 10 yrs later. I’m about to turn 30 and he’a been my best buddy for over a decade now. #adoptdontshop #animalwelfareleague

video_name: George hates being treated like a dog I am well aware. I put him on #tiktoklive while letting him out front on the leash this morning. He hasnt been leashed in months. someone seemed mad that i encoraged him to walk instead of just laying there, said “don’t treat him like a dog”. Uh don’t treat ME like a dog giving me commands and reprimanding me in my live. This is my pet peeve, ppl telling me what to do like I am anyone’s personal entertainment monkey. Negative comments will be muted and if its bad enough will get the block. Plz sit back and enjoy the work it takes to share my pet joy for others online.

video_name: an American tourist is shocked by how low hotel prices are inside of China 🇨🇳  This is Livefortuna Hotel in Beijing China and it’s hard to believe this is only $80 compared to it’s equivalent in the United States. Here you have a 2 person room with a living room, kitchen, free laundry, swimming pool, and gigantic gym. For many years in the United States hotels have been criticized for their value compared to the price people are paying. It’s hard to imagine a place like this existing for this price back in America #fyp #tellme #traveltiktok #china #beijing

video_name: A 26 year old American tourist is in disbelief by Robot workers in China 🇨🇳  This is in Beijing China at the famous Robot Mall. This mall can be found on the outskirts of the city and features an entire mall just of robots. Here they showcase Chinas robot and AI technology.  Not only are there shops with robot workers, but also pet robots, robot fishes, and even sport robots. It’s an absolutely bizarre yet fascinating scene and while visiting this mall I was the only American at the time #fyp #tellme #traveltiktok #china #beijing

video_name: A 26 year old American YouTuber describes the safety of traveling through China 🇨🇳 This was filmed in Beijing, China in the China Southern Airport lounge. Many people do not believe the reality of what it is like in China. China has incredible airports, that are both modern and clean.  Additionally a common question that I receive, is it safe to travel to China as an American ? Over 2 million American tourists visit China every year, it is completely safe and easy. There is no requirements for transfers through the airport and now USA passport holders can visit China visa free for 10 days #fyp #tellme #traveltiktok #china #beijing

video_name: An American tourist is left speechless after he finds himself alone on the Great Wall of China 🇨🇳  This shocking video shows the wonder of the world almost completely empty. One of the most famous landmarks in the world seems to have no visitors. At 1st I could not believe it, it felt like we were in an amusement park all to ourselves.  Of course there are other tourists here but maybe only a few hundred on this giant wall. You can walk for almost 10 minutes and not run into another person. Also what was strange is the price is so low to enter, only $5. I’m not sure what is happening here #fyp #tellme #traveltiktok #china #beijing

video_name: 26 year old full time American traveler shows reality of the Great Wall of China 🇨🇳  This video was filmed in Beijing China, as part of a $5 Great Wall of China tour. I found this tour on a website and let me tell you it was great. They picked us up at a meeting point in downtown Beijing.  Took us to the Great Wall which is about 1.5 hour drive and then provided snacks, drinks and an explanation. Now you do have to pay for your own gondola which is $10 but it’s worth it. The Great Wall is an amazing wonder of the world but you definitely need to be in shape to enjoy it #fyp #tellme #traveltiktok #china #beijing

video_name: American traveler shows what it is really like inside Chinas famous Panda city 🇨🇳 This is inside Chengdu China, a city that is the Panda capital of the world. The entire city is decorated in pandas, from shops, advertisements, buildings. If you love pandas then you will love Chengdu  This is the Panda sanctuary and entrance to this park is less than $10. It is shocking how affordable prices are here in China compared to both Europe and the US. Uber’s are less than $5, tickets are less than $10, hotels are under $30, and meals are under $5 #fyp #tellme #traveltiktok #china #chengdu

video_name: An American travel describes his experience as a foreigner inside of China 🇨🇳  One thing many people do not know about China is how they will treat foreigners and tourists. Especially those from America. For many years we have been told not to visit China but why?  My experience in China has been very surprising. Everyone is very friendly and more importantatly curious. However my experience in hotels is shocking. The value of $25 hotels in China cannot even compare to $100 hotels in the USA. Especially the customer service #fyp #tellme #traveltiktok #china #beijing

bio: 🎁 Taller gratuito: “3 verdades sobre la ansiedad que nadie te cuenta👇
video_name: ¡Hola, mis exploradores del alma! 🌟 En este vídeo os voy a contar el origen del rechazo y del abandono —dos heridas emocionales que muchos llevamos dentro sin darnos cuenta, pero que influyen muchísimo en cómo nos relacionamos, en lo que sentimos y hasta en cómo nos vemos a nosotros mismos. Así que si alguna vez has sentido que no eras suficiente, que te dejaban de lado, o que el miedo a perder a alguien te paraliza… quédate, porque esto te va a resonar. Vamos a explorar juntos desde dónde nace todo esto.

bio: 🎁 Taller gratuito: “3 verdades sobre la ansiedad que nadie te cuenta👇
video_name: La ansiedad siempre llega primero. Se cuela en la mente disfrazada de urgencia, hablándote en susurros que se sienten como gritos: ¿Y si no es suficiente? ¿Y si te equivocas? ¿Y si todo se cae? Habla con miedo, con prisa, con necesidad de controlar. Es ruidosa. Insistente. Agotadora. Quiere respuestas inmediatas, garantías, certezas imposibles. Pero si te das un respiro… si dejas de correr detrás de cada pensamiento… algo más profundo se hace presente. La intuición. Ella no compite por tu atención. No grita. No exige. Solo espera. Y cuando la ansiedad termina de hablar, la intuición responde, suave pero firme: Esto ya lo sabes. Confía en ti. El camino no se ve claro, pero lo estás pisando. Y en ese instante… hay calma. Porque entendés que la ansiedad viene del miedo, pero la intuición nace de la verdad.

bio: 🎁 Taller gratuito: “3 verdades sobre la ansiedad que nadie te cuenta👇
video_name: ¡Hola, mis exploradores del alma! 🌿 En este vídeo os comparto las 3 verdades que nunca voy a olvidar y que cambiaron por completo mi forma de ver el dolor. Si estás cansado de sufrir, de darle vueltas a todo y sentir que nada cambia… quédate, porque estas tres verdades me ayudaron a soltar, a entender y a empezar a vivir con más calma. No son mágicas, pero sí muy reales. Y cuando las integras… todo empieza a tener otro sentido.

bio: 🎁 Taller gratuito: “3 verdades sobre la ansiedad que nadie te cuenta👇
video_name: En este vídeo te voy a contar el secreto para empezar a vencer el miedo y la ansiedad. No es magia, ni fórmulas raras… es algo simple, pero que nadie nos enseña. Y cuando lo entiendes, todo empieza a cambiar

bio: 🎁 Taller gratuito: “3 verdades sobre la ansiedad que nadie te cuenta👇
video_name: ¿Te cuesta encontrar calma aunque lo intentes todo? Respiras, meditas, haces deporte… pero dentro sigue el ruido. Tal vez no es tu mente la que está saturada. Tal vez es tu cuerpo el que guarda los bloqueos que no estás viendo. En este vídeo te cuento los 7 bloqueos físicos que están saboteando tu paz emocional… y cómo empezar a liberarlos.

bio: 🎁 Taller gratuito: “3 verdades sobre la ansiedad que nadie te cuenta👇
video_name: Os voy a decir algo que entendí después de una ruptura…” Una ruptura no duele tanto por quien se va. Duele por lo que esa persona tocó dentro de ti. Si te hizo daño, lo que realmente arde no es solo lo que pasó… es la herida que ya llevabas desde antes: el miedo al abandono, el sentir que no eras suficiente, la soledad que ya estaba ahí. Esa persona solo lo activó. No lo creó. Por eso, cuando alguien se va y te rompe, no estás perdiendo el amor de tu vida. Estás viendo la parte de ti que aún necesita tu propio amor. Y ahí empieza la verdadera sanación: cuando dejas de mirar fuera, y empiezas a abrazar lo que dentro pide ser visto.

bio: 🎁 Taller gratuito: “3 verdades sobre la ansiedad que nadie te cuenta👇
video_name: A veces decimos “todo va a estar bien” como si fuera un mantra sagrado. Pero la verdad es que muchas veces no lo decimos desde la fe real, sino desde el miedo. Como si fuera una frase mágica para evitar que las cosas se desmoronen. No confiamos, necesitamos convencernos. Y ahí es donde la fe se empieza a sentir como una cárcel. Porque cuando crees solo para no sufrir, para no equivocarte, para no “caer en desgracia”… en realidad no estás creyendo. Estás obedeciendo al miedo. Estás buscando seguridad, no conexión. La fe vivida desde el miedo se convierte en una especie de trato forzado con el universo: “yo me porto bien, tú me cuidas”. Pero eso no es amor, eso es control disfrazado. La fe que libera no exige perfección, no pide garantías. Es esa voz tranquila que dice “aunque no entienda, estoy en paz”. No porque tengas todo resuelto, sino porque confías en algo más grande —y también en ti. Cuando la fe nace del amor, no te encierra. Te abre. Te acompaña, no te vigila. Te sostiene, no te amenaza.

bio: 🎁 Taller gratuito: “3 verdades sobre la ansiedad que nadie te cuenta👇
video_name: Siempre queremos lo que no tenemos. Y cuando lo tenemos, ya estamos pensando en lo que sigue. ¿Sabes por qué? Porque no vivimos desde la conciencia, vivimos desde la carencia. Nos desconectamos tanto del presente, que no reconocemos el valor de lo que ya está. La calma, la plenitud, la claridad… no están en lo que falta, están en aprender a estar.

video_name: 📌 Detail fakta: Nama: Survival di bawah es Sumber Video: Zack D Films Lokasi: Danau dan sungai beku di wilayah musim dingin Tahun: Fakta umum sepanjang sejarah musim dingin Status: Fakta yang sering diajarkan dalam pelatihan survival Saat berjalan di atas permukaan es, risiko terbesar adalah retakan yang bisa membuat seseorang jatuh ke air dingin di bawahnya. Dalam kondisi ini, tindakan pertama yang penting dilakukan adalah merentangkan tangan selebar mungkin. Gerakan ini bisa membantu menahan tubuh agar tidak langsung tenggelam sepenuhnya, sekaligus memberi pegangan di permukaan es. Banyak penyintas yang selamat berkat refleks sederhana ini. Namun, bila seseorang terjatuh ke dalam air, situasinya bisa jauh lebih berbahaya. Air yang sangat dingin bisa membuat tubuh syok, otot kaku, dan pikiran panik. Dalam keadaan bingung, orang sering kehilangan arah, tidak tahu lagi mana permukaan atas. Beberapa kasus mencatat, korban justru berenang menjauh dari lubang tempat mereka jatuh, membuat mereka terjebak di bawah lapisan es yang tertutup rapat. Cara terbaik dalam situasi ini adalah melawan kepanikan. Tarik napas sedalam mungkin, usahakan tetap tenang, lalu fokus mencari sumber cahaya. Cahaya dari luar biasanya menembus tipis permukaan es, dan itu menjadi penanda arah menuju lubang keluar. Dengan mengikuti cahaya, peluang menemukan jalur selamat jadi lebih besar. Setelah berhasil mencapai lubang, jangan langsung mencoba berdiri. Tubuh yang basah dan lemah bisa membuat es di sekitarnya kembali pecah. Sebaliknya, merayaplah perlahan dengan posisi tubuh rata di permukaan es, lalu geser perlahan ke arah yang lebih tebal sebelum benar-benar berdiri. Banyak pelatihan survival menekankan pentingnya latihan mental menghadapi keadaan darurat ini. Keberanian dan ketenangan justru bisa lebih menyelamatkan dibanding kekuatan fisik semata. Itulah sebabnya pengetahuan sederhana seperti mencari cahaya di bawah es sering kali menjadi perbedaan antara hidup dan mati. #faktaunik #fakesituation  #kisahnyata #fakebodyy⚠️  #fakesituation⚠️
